# Noetfield public site — verdict gate (NOOS integrator)

**Research is input, not output.** Never transfer audit/research findings directly onto noetfield.com or bulk HTML in `Noetfield/`.

## Goal

Public www must stand with best-in-market competitors on **honesty, clarity, and buyer conversion** — not on fabricated proof, internal jargon, or raw research pasted as copy.

## Required pipeline (Track B — UPG-NF-PUB-01/02)

```
Research / external audit
  → Verdict doc (ACCEPT | REJECT | DEFER per finding)
  → Claim–evidence matrix (every strong claim → source or remove)
  → CTA journey map
  → Claim-risk matrix P0–P3
  → Prioritized fix list
  → P0 www edits only (Small Fix Rule)
  → Founder gate for copy/IA redesign (P1+)
  → Receipt + deploy
```

## Machine-safe outputs (noetfeld-OS / receipts)

- Route inventory, claim matrix, CTA map, risk matrix, fix list → `receipts/proof/` or `docs/_NOOS_AGENT/` only.
- **Forbidden:** implementing audit copy suggestions in Noetfield repo from NOOS lane without founder verdict.

## PR discipline (when coordinating Noetfield PRs)

- **Split:** tech/verify/CI/asset pins (merge) vs copy/IA (hold until verdict).
- **Never merge** bulk homepage rewrites titled "per external audit" without claim-evidence sign-off.

## P0 only on www (without founder)

Remove fake claims, fix broken links/routes, stale asset pins, internal language leaks — not redesign from research.

## No interactive downgrade (CRITICAL — Noetfield R-012)

When coordinating Noetfield www PRs: **never** remove or shrink live demo/sandbox hooks (`nfSsotDemo`, `nf26-demoStepper`, `nfLiveProofForm`, agent trace, trial evaluate) to pass audit, copy, or asset-pin lanes. Require `scripts/verify-www-interactive-fidelity.sh` PASS before merge. Static `nf-workspace-mock` is not a real client sandbox.

